OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,FThe First Minister has been accused of
OL,7,Fbeing "distracted" by independence and
OL,8,Fconstitutional issues rather than
OL,9,Ftopics like healthcare and education.
OL,11,FReform in Wales' Leader Dan Thomas
OL,12,Ftold Senedd Members on Tuesday (19
OL,13,FMay) that he had been "disappointed"
OL,14,Fto hear that Welsh independence and a
OL,15,Fpush for more devolved powers had been
OL,16,Ftopics of Rhun ap Iorwerth's initial
OL,17,Fconversations with Keir Starmer.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
