FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,FMr ap Iorwerth reiterated to the
OL,7,Fchamber that he had told the Prime
OL,8,FMinister that he expected Wales to be
OL,9,Ftreated as an "equal partner" by the
OL,10,FUK Government.
OL,12,FMr ap Iorwerth said: "I was pleased to
OL,13,Fspeak with Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,14,Flast week to set out the importance I
OL,15,Fplace on a constructive relationship
OL,16,Fwith the UK Government, and to press
OL,17,Fthe case for further discussion on how
OL,18,Fgreater devolution and fair funding
OL,19,Fcan improve the lives of the people of
OL,20,FWales.
OL,26,@tD@VOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,F"As I have emphasised many times, I
OL,7,Fexpect our nation to be treated as an
OL,8,Fequal partner in those discussions,
OL,9,Fand for the actions which follow from
OL,10,Fthe UK Government to reflect that in
OL,11,Freality, not just in rhetoric.
OL,13,F"Claiming that this is a union of
OL,14,Fequals is not enough because any
OL,15,Fanalysis of the reality leaves such
OL,16,Fwords ringing hollow."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,FHowever the Reform Leader challenged
OL,7,FMr ap Iorwerth on his pursuit of
OL,8,Fconstitutional issues, like
OL,9,Findependence, saying they appeared to
OL,10,Fbe a "distraction" in his
OL,11,Fconversations with - who he described
OL,12,Fas - the "outgoing Prime Minister".
OL,14,FMr Thomas said: "Hopes and platitudes
OL,15,Fmay strike a chord during the election
OL,16,Fcampaign but governing Wales requires
OL,17,Fministerial leadership, delivery and
OL,18,Fresults.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,F"That is why I was disappointed to
OL,7,Fread reports that one of your first
OL,8,Fdiscussions with the outgoing Prime
OL,9,FMinister touched on independence.
OL,11,F"Most people in Wales are asking far
OL,12,Fmore basic questions: can I get a GP
OL,13,Fappointment, will my child receive a
OL,14,Fdecent education, can I afford my
OL,15,Fbills, will my family have
OL,16,Fopportunities in Wales in four year's
OL,17,Ftime?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,F"These are the issues that matter and
OL,7,Fwhile your statement today implies
OL,8,Fthat these are your priorities,
OL,9,Fraising independence with the UK
OL,10,FGovernment suggests that you are
OL,11,Fdistracted by constitutional issues.
OL,13,F"It appears that the only topic the
OL,14,FPrime Minister is prepared to discuss
OL,15,Fin the future is devolution, so people
OL,16,Facross Wales will understandably ask -
OL,17,Fwhere is the progress on funding,
OL,18,Fwhere is the progress on rail?"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,FThe First Minister argued that he is
OL,7,F"obsessed" with aspects like devolving
OL,8,Fmore powers because theses are the
OL,9,F"tools" needed to bring progress.
OL,11,FHe said: "The accusation is often made
OL,12,Fthat there's an obsession with the
OL,13,Fconstitution. I'm obsessed with doing
OL,14,Fthe right thing for Wales, I'm
OL,15,Fobsessed with taking our nation
OL,16,Fforward and that means getting the
OL,17,Fright tools in our hands to do the job.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,F"I'll give you an analogy, you want to
OL,7,Fput a cupboard up - your screwdriver
OL,8,Fis broken. We need the tools to do the
OL,9,Fjob but you you continue to struggle
OL,10,Fon with a broken screwdriver. Let's
OL,11,Fmake the old screwdriver great again!
OL,13,F"Let's get the right tools to do that
OL,14,Fjob and that is all we are talking
OL,15,Fabout when we talk about expanding the
OL,16,Fpowers that we have."
OL,18,FOn independence, he added that he was
OL,19,F"setting a journey" and the "people of
OL,20,FWales will decide the pace" of that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
