PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1779447783
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of being
OL,4,C'distracted' by independence
OL,6,FThe First Minister addressed the
OL,7,Fchamber to outline his priorities in
OL,8,Fgovernment. They include cutting
OL,9,Fwaiting lists, raising standards in
OL,10,Fschools, creating jobs, tackling child
OL,11,Fpoverty, helping households with the
OL,12,Fcost-of-living crisis and "standing up
OL,13,Ffor Wales".
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
